 <title>BADCamp Behind the Scenes</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/badcamp-behind-scenes</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Come join the BADCamp organizing collective as we share why and how we plan, organize and deliver the camp. Expect an irreverent but honest discussion about the ins and outs of raising funds, securing facilities, building convention websites, organizing volunteers, eating tons of vegan Vietnamese food, designing things at absolute last minute, playing various board games both competitively and cooperatively, and most importantly achieving consensus among a diverse but friendly group of like-minded peers. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/business-community&quot;&gt;Business + Community&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/eatings&quot; class=&quot;user user-43 entityreference&quot;&gt;eatings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/aimeerae&quot; class=&quot;user user-34 entityreference&quot;&gt;aimeerae&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/andrewmallis&quot; class=&quot;user user-25 entityreference&quot;&gt;Andrew_Mallis&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/annabella&quot; class=&quot;user user-17 entityreference&quot;&gt;Annabella&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/carsonblack&quot; class=&quot;user user-9 entityreference&quot;&gt;carsonblack&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/darius&quot; class=&quot;user user-2 entityreference&quot;&gt;darius&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/fluxsauce&quot; class=&quot;user user-1 entityreference&quot;&gt;fluxsauce&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/jenlampton&quot; class=&quot;user user-13 entityreference&quot;&gt;jenlampton&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/kmiller&quot; class=&quot;user user-773 entityreference&quot;&gt;kmiller&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/megh&quot; class=&quot;user user-5 entityreference&quot;&gt;Megh&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/populist&quot; class=&quot;user user-28 entityreference&quot;&gt;populist&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/sfbob&quot; class=&quot;user user-16 entityreference&quot;&gt;sfbob&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-date-and-time field-type-datetime field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session date and time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Sunday, October 25, 2015 - 11:00am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-time-slot field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session time slot: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/time-slot/1100am-1200pm&quot;&gt;11:00am - 12:00pm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-room field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session room: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/rooms/gold-usc-career-center&quot;&gt;GOLD - USC Career Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
