 <title>The continuous integration / continuous happiness workflow</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/continuous-integration-continuous-happiness-workflow</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Continuous integration (CI) has been a floating buzzword for quite some time now. While it is widely accepted by developers and devops engineers, its value is often overlooked or misunderstood. This session aims to explain the benefits of a good CI process from the perspective of a business (website owners). CI offers continuous delivery, empowers a collaborative environment and delivers superior project quality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This session will demonstrate some real use cases where the continuous integration process contributes to the project success and ultimately business success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/business-community&quot;&gt;Business + Community&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/xcf33&quot; class=&quot;user user-161 entityreference&quot;&gt;xcf33&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/ygerasimov&quot; class=&quot;user user-747 entityreference&quot;&gt;ygerasimov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-date-and-time field-type-datetime field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session date and time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Saturday, October 24, 2015 - 10:00am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-time-slot field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session time slot: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links 