 <title>Technical Pollution: Insights from the Lorax</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/technical-pollution-insights-lorax</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical debt is a common analogy to describe the cost of code mess and poor architecture. However, how far can the monetary analogy go? In this session we will look at insights from the Lorax and “environmental debt”. Specifically, we will build an argument for why the monetary comparison communicates the wrong idea about how technical debt is measured and how it impacts business. We will conclude with identifying measures and practices to mitigate technical debt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This session might be for you if you deal with the challenge of communicating the business cost of technical debt, you want a clearer understanding of what technical debt is and how to measure it, or you want advice on how to mitigate against technical debt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The key takeaway from this session will be an improved strategy for identifying, measuring, preventing, and communicating technical debt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/coding-development&quot;&gt;Coding + Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/intermediate&quot;&gt;Intermediate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/zendoodles&quot; class=&quot;user user-189 entityreference&quot;&gt;ZenDoodles&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/josephdpurcell&quot; class=&quot;user user-193 entityreference&quot;&gt;josephdpurcell&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-date-and-time field-type-datetime field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session date and time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Saturday, October 24, 2015 - 9:00am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-time-slot field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session time slot: &lt;/h2&gt;